<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Accès Restreint - EventHINT</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=clash-display@400,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    fontFamily: {
                        'clash': ['"Clash Display"', 'sans-serif'],
                        'manrope': ['Manrope', 'sans-serif'],
                    },
                    colors: {
                        'primary': '#8B5CF6',
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-black text-white font-manrope flex items-center justify-center h-screen">
    <div class="bg-gray-900 p-8 shadow-lg rounded-lg text-center max-w-md w-full">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-clash font-bold text-red-500">Accès Restreint</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-white/70">Votre compte a été suspendu. Veuillez contacter le support pour plus d'informations.</p>
        <button class="mt-6 bg-primary text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-purple-500 transition-colors">
            Essayer de vous inscrire de nouveau !
        </button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>